  "title": "Food & Beverage Ambassador",
  "description": "<p><strong>ATTENTION </strong>independent free spirits who thrive on friendship, community and new experiences!</p><p><br /></p><p>M Social Singapore is characteristically scouting for the curious, the explorers and the ones who dare to dream. We seek sanguine individuals who are expressive with a touch of creativity. Leave the stiff handshakes behind. Let’s make some memories together. Join our M Socialite movement.</p><p><br /></p><p>Wait no further, M Social Casting Call – <strong>Food & Beverage Ambassador</strong> is now open!</p><p><br /></p><p>The role reports to the F&B Manager and <strong>YOU</strong> are responsible for the following;-</p><ul><li>Be a host to allocate appropriate seats to guests</li><li>To provide excellent service on dining experience to guests</li><li>Mingle and chat with guests</li><li>Proactive and highly responsive to guests’ needs and ensure their satisfaction</li><li>Learn the menu and offer suggestions and recommendations such as wine pairing</li><li>Arrange table setting according to meal types and prepare turnover for next guest</li><li>In charge of training part-timers on duty</li><li>Maintain cleanliness of the outlet and ensure service counters are presentable at all times</li><li>To carry out any other duties and responsibilities as assigned</li><li>Ballet Dancing (Just kidding!)</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>So what’s the requirements?</p><ul><li>Cheerful, outgoing and energetic</li><li>Good Interpersonal and Communication skills</li><li>Team player in a diverse work environment</li><li>Great attention to details</li><li>Proactive approach towards guests</li><li>Able to commit to regular part-time work schedules</li><li>Have Food and Hygiene certificate</li><li>Ability to stand and walk for extended periods</li><li>Proficient time-management skills</li><li>Procifient with maintaining solid customer base</li><li>Available to work shifts, extended hours, over weekends and holidays</li><li>Be fun and outgoing!</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Time and tide wait for no man, hurry send in your application NOW!</p><p>Human Resources</p><p>M Social Singapore</p><p>90 Robertson Quay</p><p>Singapore 238259</p><p><em>e-mail address: jolie.yee@millenniumhotels.com</em></p><p><em>We apologise that only shortlisted applicants will be notified.</em></p>",
